---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Guzman Tax Accounting & Multi Services – Las Vegas, NV" description="Professional tax and accounting services in Las Vegas for the Latino community. Tax preparation, bookkeeping, LLC and more. Spanish-speaking staff available." lang="en" langHref="/" hreflangEs="https://guzmantaxaccounting.com/" hreflangEn="https://guzmantaxaccounting.com/en/">

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content fade-in">
      <p class="eyebrow">Bilingual Accounting Firm · Las Vegas, NV</p>
      <h1>Professional <span>Tax & Accounting</span> Services in Las Vegas</h1>
      <p>Personalized service in English and Spanish for individuals, families, and businesses. No hidden fees, no surprises — real results.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="tel:+17253406758" class="btn btn-primary">Call Now</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/17253406758" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-badges">
        <div class="hero-badge"><span><strong>239+</strong> Projects Completed</span></div>
        <div class="hero-badge"><span><strong>24/7</strong> Bilingual Support</span></div>
        <div class="hero-badge"><span><strong>10+</strong> Years Experience</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section"><div class="container">
  <div class="section-header text-center"><p class="eyebrow">What We Do</p><h2>Our Tax & Accounting Expertise</h2><p>Complete solutions for your tax and financial situation, explained in your language.</p></div>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 3H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v16a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h10a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V9z"/><path d="M14 3v6h6"/></svg></div><h3>Tax Preparation</h3><p>Personal and business taxes: 1040, LLC, S-Corp, C-Corp. We maximize your refund legally.</p><a href="/en/taxes" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block;">Learn more →</a></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4" y1="20" x2="20" y2="20"/><line x1="7" y1="20" x2="7" y2="14"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="9"/><line x1="17" y1="20" x2="17" y2="4"/></svg></div><h3>Bookkeeping</h3><p>Monthly reconciliation, accounting records and clear financial statements for your business.</p><a href="/en/services" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block;">Learn more →</a></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="3.5"/><path d="M4 20c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8s8 3.6 8 8"/></svg></div><h3>Payroll Services</h3><p>Payroll processing, W-2, 1099, direct deposit and federal/state tax compliance.</p><a href="/en/services" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block;">Learn more →</a></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L20.5 7v10L12 22 3.5 17V7z"/></svg></div><h3>LLC Formation</h3><p>We help you form your LLC correctly, including EIN, operating agreement and state compliance.</p><a href="/en/services" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block;">Learn more →</a></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="13" rx="1"/><path d="M3 7l9 7 9-7"/></svg></div><h3>IRS Letters & Audits</h3><p>Response and representation for IRS letters, audits and tax compliance support.</p><a href="/en/services" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block;">Learn more →</a></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="14" rx="1"/><line x1="2" y1="8" x2="22" y2="8"/></svg></div><h3>Web Design & E-Commerce</h3><p>Free 1-page website when you create an LLC or hire our services. Hosting included.</p><a href="/en/services" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block;">Learn more →</a></div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center" style="margin-top:40px;"><a href="/en/services" class="btn btn-outline">View All Services</a></div>
</div></section>

<section class="stats-section"><div class="container"><div class="stats-grid">
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="number" data-target="239" data-suffix="+">239+</span><span class="label">Projects Completed</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="number">24/7</span><span class="label">Bilingual Support</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="number" data-target="10" data-suffix="+">10+</span><span class="label">Years of Experience</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="number">100%</span><span class="label">Personalized Service</span></div>
</div></div></section>

<section class="cta-section"><div class="container">
  <p class="eyebrow text-center" style="color:var(--primary);">Ready to get started?</p>
  <h2>Schedule Your Free Consultation Today</h2>
  <p>No commitment. We explain everything you need to know about your taxes or business.</p>
  <div class="btn-group">
    <a href="/en/free-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
    <a href="tel:+17253406758" class="btn btn-white">Call: (725) 340-6758</a>
  </div>
</div></section>

</Layout>
